title: CHEAP!!!
app_fee: If interested, applicant pays for credit and character checks.
posting_body: ['This 2nd floor apartment overlooks a beautiful quiet street in the heart of Bucktown.', 'It is close to everything :  schools, shopping, buses, the  Blue Line, restaurants, a great night life, etc.', 'In this vintage apartment, the  bedrooms are small, but the kitchen and frontroom are large.', ' The bathroom has a shower, but no tub.', 'There is a large covered back porch that can be used  for extra storage or  living space.', ' All rooms have been newly painted.', ' The neighbors and owners are nice.', " It's a great place to live in one of Chicago's greatest neighborhoods, inexpensively.", 'For more information call Linda at 847-208-6773.', 'Open house will be this Sunday, June 26th, from 1 to 4.', ' Occupancy:  AUGUST 1st.', 'Thanks.']
